# hello_world.gos - Geometry OS Script
# Phase 30: Spatial "Hello World"

## Bytecode

```
0x01 0x48 0x65 0x6C 0x6C 0x6F  # LoadConst "Hello"
0x01 0x20 0x57 0x6F 0x72 0x6C  # LoadConst " Worl"
0x01 0x64 0x00 0x00 0x00 0x00  # LoadConst "d"
0x40                            # Print
0x3F                            # Halt
```

## Spatial Assembly

```
; Data Section (Layer 0)
@data:0x00  "Hello"  ; DataPillar at (0,0)
@data:0x18  " Worl"  ; DataPillar at (24,0)
@data:0x30  "d"      ; DataPillar at (48,0)

; Logic Section (Layer 1)
@logic:0x48 CONCAT   ; LogicGate at (72,0)

; Output Section (Layer 2)
@io:0x60 PRINT       ; OutputBridge at (96,0)

; Control Section (Layer 2)
@ctrl:0x78 HALT      ; Terminator at (120,0)

; Connections
CONNECT @data:0x00 -> @data:0x18
CONNECT @data:0x18 -> @data:0x30
CONNECT @data:0x30 -> @logic:0x48
CONNECT @logic:0x48 -> @io:0x60
CONNECT @io:0x60 -> @ctrl:0x78
```

## Visual Map

```
     0    24   48   72   96   120
  0  ┌────┬────┬────┬────┬────┬────┐
     │    │    │    │    │    │    │
 24  │ D  │ D  │ D  │ L  │ O  │ T  │
     │ A  │ A  │ A  │ O  │ U  │ E  │
 48  │ T  │ T  │ T  │ G  │ T  │ R  │
     │ A  │ A  │ A  │ I  │ P  │ M  │
 72  └────┴────┴────┴────┴────┴────┘

Legend:
- DATA (Blue): String storage
- LOGI (Cyan): Concatenation gate
- OUTP (Green): Output bridge (hollow)
- TERM (Red): Halt marker
```

## Execution Trace

```
T=0:   Load "Hello"    → DATA_PILLAR_0 activates (blue pulse)
T=1:   Load " Worl"    → DATA_PILLAR_1 activates (blue pulse)
T=2:   Load "d"        → DATA_PILLAR_2 activates (blue pulse)
T=3:   Logic Path      → Signal travels through yellow path
T=4:   Concat          → LOGIC_GATE combines strings
T=5:   Output          → OUTPUT_BRIDGE fires (green flash)
T=6:   Neural Gateway  → "[VOICE]: Hello World (Spatial Verification: 100%)"
T=7:   Halt            → TERMINATOR marks end (red glow)
```

## GQR Seal (Optional)

After successful execution, seal as single command:

```
SEAL "hello_world" AS GQR_EXECUTABLE
  OPCODE: 0x61 (CallGqr)
  PAYLOAD: <compressed bytecode>
  COHERENCE: 1.00
  SIGNATURE: <awaiting Z-pattern>
```

## Usage

```bash
# Transpile to spatial map
cargo run --bin spatial-interpreter -- hello_world.gos --output map.png

# Execute on GPU
cargo run --bin gpu-executor -- map.png

# Seal as GQR
cargo run --bin gqr-seal -- hello_world.gos --name "hello_world"
```

